    <div class="legend-item"><span class="badge b-fail">&#10007; fail</span> VC covered, test failed</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><span class="badge b-uncovered">&#8212; uncovered</span> No scenario written yet</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><span class="badge b-drifted">&#8635; drifted</span> Criteria changed since baseline</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><span class="badge b-manual">&#9995; manual</span> Analysis or Inspection method</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><span class="badge b-deferred">&#9201; deferred</span> Planned for a future release</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><span class="badge b-orphaned">? orphaned</span> References a deleted requirement</div>
    <h4 style="margin-top:12px">Glossary</h4>
