    <div class="legend-item" style="flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:2px"><strong>Gate A &mdash; Coverage</strong><span style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-muted)">Every VC must have at least one Gherkin scenario.</span></div>
    <div class="legend-item" style="flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:2px"><strong>Gate B &mdash; Drift</strong><span style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-muted)">Detects when criteria text changes between model versions.</span></div>
    <div class="legend-item" style="flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:2px"><strong>Gate C &mdash; Orphans</strong><span style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-muted)">Finds tests referencing requirements that no longer exist.</span></div>
    <div class="legend-item" style="flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:2px"><strong>SBOM</strong><span style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-muted)">Software Bill of Materials &mdash; inventory of all software components.</span></div>
